data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to 6815 N Central Avenue, an enchanting bungalow nestled in the heart of Seminole Heights, a historic neighborhood. This meticulously cared-for home seamlessly marries classic architectural details with modern comforts, creating a warm and inviting ambiance.  Step onto the welcoming front porch and be transported into a world of character and charm.  Natural light pours in through generous newer windows, enhancing the sense of space throughout the living areas. High ceilings and an open layout foster an airy and inviting atmosphere. Enjoy time around the wood burning fireplace or entertain your friends and loved ones in the expansive open kitchen.   The kitchen, beautifully updated, features stainless steel appliances, abundant cabinet space, and a practical breakfast bar – a perfect blend of function and style, ideal for both everyday living and entertaining.    The upstairs master retreat features a large ensuite bathroom, walk-in closet, bonus storage area, and plantation shutters, all tastefully done.  Two comfortable bedrooms downstairs offer ample closet space, promising restful nights and refreshed mornings in these peaceful retreats.  The massive attached garage allows plenty of roof for you vehicles, toys, or build out a workshop to enjoy the hobbies of your choice.     A private and fenced backyard sanctuary beckons,an idyllic backdrop for outdoor gatherings and moments of relaxation. More than enough room for a pool!    Seminole Heights invites exploration with its tree-lined streets, local eateries, and vibrant arts and culture scene. Situated just moments from downtown Tampa, you'll relish city amenities while savoring the tranquility of a residential haven.    With major roadways and public transportation within easy reach, commuting is seamless, offering convenient access to the best of Tampa Bay. This home is turnkey (Roof, HVAC, Water Heather all 2016) and ready for its new owner!
